I suggest playing a shaman, they really rock at pvp.<br>
INT-Casters are really weak at defense, and can be killed pretty easily.<br>
Melees are really bad at keeping people from running away.<br>
Hybrids are great for duels as well as pvp.<br>
<br>
Shamen have decent hit points, armor class, dots, nukes, and a fun little pet.  I'd say the same for druids, but they have no way of lowering resists, and they just plain suxor(i hate them).<br>
<br>
As for what i do on rallos - i basicly play the game like everyone on a blue server - with the added flavor of always watching my back for potential predators or prey.  The use of PvP in resolving problems is always fun, though many mid levelers are scared to ruin reputation over a disagreement.<br>
<br>
