classes.  shaman, like cylant said, is pretty good.  my personal favorites are druid(my main), SK, and monk.  druids basically because they can do a little bit of anything.  sow, snare, buffs, DS(one of your best weapons aginst melees), and all the other stuff that makes them so good at PvE as well.  SK because its basically a warrior with casting ability.  darkness, lifetaps, DoT's plus a good ammount of HP, make it vary hard to both kill and escape you.  monks are just awsome.  with fast weapons its almost impossible for a cster chanell a spell off onto you.  one of the best offensive PvP classes.  your dammage is just so amazeing from all angles (as opposed with back only for rogues) makes you hard to stop.  <br>
